---
title: Loaded Tex-Mex Beef Jacket Potatoes with Sour Cream & Sweetcorn Salad
description: Thought jacket potatoes were out of the running for weeknights? Not at all! You can cut the long baking time by halving them, then zapping in the microwave before they go in the oven. Here, we're loading them with spiced beef, sour cream and Cheddar.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mexican-beef-cheats-loaded-jacket-potatoes-cae45da2.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/mexican-beef-cheats-loaded-jacket-potatoes-5e7aed4eb5959c517f1ebc82-6b8e14f4.pdf
course: main course
